/li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-auto3-16\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto3_16-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto3_16-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Fischer 2008, p 57</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-17\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-17\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Fischer 2008, p 45</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-18\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-18\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Fischer 2008, p 43</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-19\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-19\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://thebrandeishoot.com/articles/3657#sthash.mGiNyyUV.dpuf\">\"The Brandeis Hoot&#160;\u00bb Hackett Fischer discusses book Champlain's Dream\"</a>. <i>thebrandeishoot.com</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=thebrandeishoot.com&amp;rft.atitle=The+Brandeis+Hoot+%C2%BB+Hackett+Fischer+discusses+book+Champlain%E2%80%99s+Dream&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fthebrandeishoot.com%2Farticles%2F3657%23sthash.mGiNyyUV.dpuf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChamplain%27s+Dream\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-auto4-20\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto4_20-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto4_20-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-debate/champlains-dream-lives-on-in-north-america/article1345919/\">\"Champlain's dream lives on in North America\"</a>. <i>The Globe and Mail</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_